---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: Contact Us
permalink: /contact/
---

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
    <p>We'd love to hear from you! Whether you have questions about our menu, want to book a private event, or just want to say hello.</p>
    
    <h3>Contact Information</h3>
    <dl>
      <dt>Phone</dt>
      <dd><a href="tel:{{ site.contact.phone }}">{{ site.contact.phone }}</a></dd>
      
      <dt>Email</dt>
      <dd><a href="mailto:{{ site.contact.email }}">{{ site.contact.email }}</a></dd>
      
      <dt>Address</dt>
      <dd>
        [Street Address]<br>
        [City, State ZIP]
      </dd>
    </dl>
    
    <h3>Follow Us</h3>
    <div class="d-flex gap-3">
      {% if site.social.facebook %}
        <a href="{{ site.social.facebook }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline-primary" aria-label="Facebook">
          <i class="fab fa-facebook fa-lg" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </a>
      {% endif %}
      {% if site.social.instagram %}
        <a href="{{ site.social.instagram }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline-primary" aria-label="Instagram">
          <i class="fab fa-instagram fa-lg" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </a>
      {% endif %}
      {% if site.social.twitter %}
        <a href="{{ site.social.twitter }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline-primary" aria-label="Twitter">
          <i class="fab fa-twitter fa-lg" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </a>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
    <h2>Hours</h2>
    <table class="table">
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Monday - Thursday</td>
          <td>[Hours]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Friday - Saturday</td>
          <td>[Hours]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Sunday</td>
          <td>[Hours]</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    
    <div class="mt-4">
      <a href="/location/" class="btn btn-primary">View Location & Map</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="mt-5 p-4 bg-light rounded">
  <h2>Private Events</h2>
  <p>Interested in hosting a private event at Supply & Demand? We offer customizable options for parties, corporate events, and special occasions.</p>
  <p>Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{ site.contact.email }}">{{ site.contact.email }}</a> or call <a href="tel:{{ site.contact.phone }}">{{ site.contact.phone }}</a> to discuss your event needs.</p>
</div>
